/*
 * This stylesheet is a combination of all the CSS files from the project.
 * It is organized to provide a clear and maintainable structure for developers and LLM coding agents.
 *
 * Structure:
 * 1. Font Declarations
 * 2. Root Variables (Colors, Spacing, etc.)
 * 3. Global Styles (Body, Box-sizing, etc.)
 * 4. Main Application Layout (Header, Footer, Dashboard, etc.)
 * 5. Shared Utility Classes (Buttons, Form Inputs, etc.)
 * 6. Tool-Specific Styles
 * - Goal Builder
 * - Homework Tracker
 * - Progress Monitor
 * - Therapy Data Session Taker
 * 7. Inline Fixes and Overrides
 * 8. Print Styles
 */

